2004-07-09 Dragan Sarbut <ds@baum.ro>
	
	* srcore/srspc.c:
	(src_speech_get_text_echo_type):
	(src_speech_get_spaces_echo_type):
	(src_speech_get_modifiers_echo_type):
	(src_speech_get_cursors_echo_type):
	Added checking for speech to be initialized.
	
	* srcore/srmain.ch:
	Using the --login option from srcore command line to let srcore know
	that it's running at login time and should try not to  work with gconf.
	
	* srcore/srmag.ch:
	Added some function to set magnifiers parameters without 
	working with gconf.
	
	* srcore/srctrl.c:
	Modified the magnifier control functions so they eill not work with 
	gconf if --login is passed in srcore's command line. Now at GDM login
	time , the magnifier can be controlled from the command layers.
	
	Patch for bug #122459

