2004-06-10 Dana Ormenisan <do@baum.ro>

	* srcore/srctrl.c:
	(src_repeat_last):
	(src_cmd_queue_process):
	(src_ctrl_init):
	(src_ctrl_terminate):
	Changed to put the comand before the last one in the command queue
	(in order to scroll on braille device).
	This command will take the last command value, with one exception:
	if the last command was "present layer changed".
	(Fixies for bug #132320).

