2004-05-24 Dana Ormenisan <do@baum.ro>
	* srlow/libsrlow/SRLow.c:
	Listen for "object:children-changed:add" and 
	"object:children-changed:removed" events.
	These events will be presented only for objects with SPI_ROLE_PAGE_TAB.  
	* srcore/default.xml.in:
	* srcore/verbose.xml.in:
	Change the presentation for "page-tab" role. Add presentation for:
	  - "focus:" event: 
	       'switch tab, <tab name>, <shortcut (if exists)>'
	  - "object:tab-added" event:
	       'create tab, <tab name>'
	  - "object:tab-removed" event:
	       'closing tab, <tab name>'.
	(Fixies for #bug 128970).              

