2004-05-18 Padraig O'Briain <padraig.obriain@sun.com>

	* kbd_mouse/libke/libke.c:
	(ke_report_keyecho_event): Remove workaround for bug #129951.
	(ke_register_keyset_item):
	(ke_layer_register_events):
	(ke_keyecho_register_events): Do not register key stroke listeners for
	modifiers SPI_KEYMASK_BUTTON1, SPI_KEYMASK_BUTTON2 or 
	SPI_KEYMASK_BUTTON3.
	(ke_user_key_list_unregister_events):
	(ke_layer_unregister_events):
	(ke_keyecho_unregister_events): Do not unregister key stroke listeners 
	for modifiers SPI_KEYMASK_BUTTON1, SPI_KEYMASK_BUTTON2 or 
	SPI_KEYMASK_BUTTON3.

	Fixes bug #129951.

