	(sro_get_header):
	Removed.
	(sro_get_column_header):
	(sro_get_row_header):
	(sro_get_cell):
	Added.
	(sro_default_get_name):
	In case of tables, check if the table has a relation with an appropriate
	label.
	
	(Fixies for #bug 137336).

