	Fixies #132285.

2004-03-04 Dana Ormenisan <do@baum.ro>

	* srcore/default.xml.in:
	* srcore/verbose.xml.in:
	Add presentation for tables. When a table is focused, gnopernicus will 
	outputs:"Table <table_name><#lines>.
	
	* srlow/libsrlow/SRObject.c,h:
	(sro_default_get_name):
	 Changed: if the table doesn't have an accessible name and/or a relation with an
	 appropriate label, the only/current focused table column name will be
	 presented as a table name.
	(sro_default_get_children_count):
	 Changed: in case of tables, this function will return the number of rows.
	(sro_get_line):
	 Added.
	 
	(Partial fixies for bug #132285).	 

