	* srcore/srmain.c:
	Changed calls of src_speech_send_chunk according with new prototype.

	* srcore/srspc.[c,h]:
	(src_speech_send_chunk):
	Modified to support a new parameter and to not simulate shutup actions.

	All changes are to implement a priority queue for speech.
	Changes fix bugs #120751, #126098 and #125404.

