	* srlow/libsrlow/screen-review.c,h:
	(srw_lines_get_n_lines):Count the number of empty lines if the SRW_ALIGNF_VSP_COUNT_LINES flag
	is set.
	Adjust SRWAccLine structure so this number can be passed to the 
	screen-review client.
	
	* srcore/srctrl.c:
	(src_flat_review_line)
	Report number of empty lines to braille, brlmon and speech.
	BUGFIX #108281 (partially; special voice for empty line(S) STILL needs 
	to be added)

