2003-04-17 Remus Draica <rd@baum.ro>

	* srutil/SREvent.c:
	Add SRMessages.h file at include section.
	(sru_terminate):
	Change compile flag ENABLE_PARANOIA with SRU_PARANOIA.

	* srutil/SRMessages.c:
	Change default value in case that environment variable
	GNOPERNICUS_DEBUG_STACK has no value.

	* srutil/SRMessages.h:
	Always compile runtime support for logging messages.
	Small changes to improve performance (improvements suggested by 
	Bill Haneman (bill.haneman@sun.com)).

