	    modifications of type (typecasting to guint32). 
	(mag_zoomers_set_crosswire_color): changes according to the above 
	    modifications of type (typecasting to guint32)
	(mag_tracking_logic): redesign.
	(mag_set_properties): a diffrent aproach in determinig what is in the 
	    visible area of the magnifier.
	
