	    of cursor_color's type.
	(magnifier_set_crosswire_color): changes according to the modifications 
	    of cursor_color's type.	
	
	*srconf/libsrconf/libsrconf.h:
	MAX_ZOOMER_FACTOR_X and  MAX_ZOOMER_FACTOR_Y values changed to 15 
	(at 16, gnome-mag crashes).
	
