	Removed unused variable 'serverhost'.

	* braille/libbrl/brlxml.c:
	Added in function 'BrailleEvents':
	    case bec_key_codes:
	    case bec_switch_pad:
	    case bec_sensor:
	    default:
		break;
	* braille/libbrl/braille.c:
	Added #include "alvabrl.h".		
	
