	Removed unused variable 'i' (line 495).
	Added in functions alva_on_keys_changed and alva_brl_send_dots:
	    case ALVADT_GENERIC:
	    default:
		break;
		
	* braille/libbrl/baumbrl.c:
	Commented out Mask16 definition (it was defined, but not used).
	Changed baum_brl_input_parser definition:
	-short baum_brl_input_parser (unsigned char)
	+short baum_brl_input_parser (int)
	
