2002-09-12 Adi Dascal <ad@baum.ro>

	* magnifier/*
	* srcore/srmag.*
	* srcore/srmain.c:
	Added magnifier.
	Differential magnification (eg. 3x horizontal, 2x vertical)
	Increase/decrease magnification commanded from keys:
	    * increase y factor mapped on "keypad Up"
	    * decrease y factor mapped on "keypad Down"
	    * increase x factor mapped on "keypad Right"
	    * decrease x factor mapped on "keypad Left"
	Follow focus for some of the roles.
