	Update the load_interface functions.

2002-08-26 Remus Draica <rd@baum.ro>
	
	* srlow/libsrlow/SRLow.c:
	Report correct user intention for text objects.
	Report NULL object in case in which no accessible object has focus.
	Add a mecanism to delay event report (used specialy in 
	state-changed-active and text-changed-delete, and also to not report all 
	events in case of large number of events when report only last).

	* srlow/libsrlow/SRObject.c:
	Add a new field to SRObject strucure to retain text deleted or inserted.

