2002-08-07 Remus Draica <rd@baum.ro>

	* srlow/libsrlow/SRObject.[c,h]:
	* srlow/libsrlow/SRLow.[c,h]:
	Replace g_assert with other other macros to avoid gnopernicus crashes.
	To have old behaviour (used in developement process) SRL_DEBUG compile
	flag must be defined in SRObject.h file. Also this flag shows memory
	leakes for allocated strings and SRObject objects.
	Remove unused code.

