	Some optimizations and API changes.

	* srlow/test/* :
	* srcore/srmain.c:
	Modified to meet libsrlow changes.

	* magnifier/magxml.c: 
	Used static keyword for better linkage.	

	* configure.in:
	Changes to support some modules modifications. Some optimization in 
	required libraries version direction.
	
