	* srcore/srmain.c:
	Removed the async queue.
	Add supprot for Braille input.

2002-03-01 Iuliu Szijjarto <is@baum.ro>

	* srconf/libsrconf/libsrconf.c
	* srconf/libsrconf/libsrconf.h
	* srconf/test/testlibsrconf.c:
	Some optimizations and API changes. Also a new functionality 
	was added srconf_set_config_data. In this way srconf supports
	two way communication.

	* kbd_mouse/libke/libke.c
	* kbd_mouse/libke/libke.h
	* kbd_mouse/test/testlibke.c:
	Modified to meet srconf changes. Also some optimizations
	were made.

	* srcore/srmain.c:
	Modified to meet srutil and srconf changes. Also exit support 
	was added via a srconf notification.

